long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This plugin is a subsidiary of FlashLabel printer, Users can connect to a thermal printer via usb to print. This Extension allows you to print the currently displayed Web Page. Although this function is very simple, , I needed to have this ability in Chrome and so I created it!You can press Ctrl + P to open the print preview interface, select printer and click Print to print the valid content.
